{"tid":27540,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（處境題）係成田機場坐skyline坐左人地個位","createTime":"2016-12-07T11:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T02:38:12.000Z","uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac6bc0dcaaca55047d9c85d09d24e77c4ce8db8","tid":27540,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"我無揀到位（用ic卡點樣揀位）<br />\n一上車我就求其搵位坐以為唔洗揀位<br />\n之後個鬼佬見到我坐左佢個位就走左去第2到坐<br />\n跟住個鬼佬就坐左人地個位<br />\n咁過左陣第三個人上車見到個鬼佬坐左佢個位咁就同個鬼佬鳩up幾句就話我坐左佢個位<br />\n咁第三個人又坐左去第二個位<br />\n咁好啦我就希望唔好再有人上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知去到下一個站成堆人上車咁第三個人就坐返鬼佬個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個鬼佬依加就坐左我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該點算<br />\n利申唔識英文"},{"pid":"dc18f84ae788cae5bf5ba2f5d3bfc9c77a0bc28c","tid":27540,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"寫住指定席自由席都你都鳩坐屌你咩"},{"pid":"2b25e6c2410dc0f3dff24f3795cf228d4a121bd8","tid":27540,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫住指定席自由席都你都鳩坐屌你咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪係第2卡有自由席<br />\n我一上車就坐低乜都無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fae6f9034e75958799f9a97a06d8fea251f3392","tid":27540,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"正所謂猛虎不及地頭蟲<br />\n呢個時候扮日本人就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c11122542f281a3637b920806cd2d8a2a486c4a","tid":27540,"uid":9919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫住指定席自由席都你都鳩坐屌你咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩上網睇全車都係指定黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b26101b7506e1e32858bb001321522a350c64e8","tid":27540,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2